cff-version: 1.2.0
message: "If you use this software or the kinase table it produces, please cite it as below."
title: "Human kinase reference table"
abstract: >-
  A reproducible R pipeline that builds a comprehensive human kinase gene table by
  integrating seven kinase resources (UniProt pkinfam, Manning/kinase.com, KinHub,
  GO molecular-function gene sets, HGNC EC 2.7 subclasses, UniProt keyword KW-0418,
  and the IDG dark kinome), keyed on base Ensembl gene IDs and typed by enzymatic
  function.
type: software
authors:
